{"type":null,"faqId":15815,"title":"亲情关怀是什么？能够解决哪些问题？","answer":"<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">亲情关怀是一款支持手机远程协助的应用，只需在手机上轻轻一点，就可以远程求助他人、或者远程帮助他人解决手机问题。就像操作自己的手机一样简单方便。</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">支持向本地联系人发起求助</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">远程查看和控制对方手机</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">远程帮助对方修改手机设置、下载安装应用程序等操作</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">远程在对方手机上涂鸦，直观指引操作</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">支持语音通话，沟通更高效</span>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">在</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">EMUI 3.0 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">系统的手机中已经预装了亲情关怀，可从桌面打开“手机服务”，点击“远程协助”直接使用。</span>\n<p>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8234","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1414658630000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,Cherry-CL20","visitedTimes":294,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}